        <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
          <div class="panel-body">
         	<b> Can I assess articles even if I don&#39;t register with JAMR?</b><br>
			Yes you can see all the articles published.<br>
			<b>Can I get the details about the article?</b><br>
			Yes you can see the article details like author&#39;s name, related subject, keywords<br>
			<b>Can I download published articles as a pdf?</b><br>
			Yes you can download an article you like as a pdf.<br>
			<b>Can I have an account by registering for free?</b><br>
			Yes it is free to register with us. <br>
			<b>Can I become an author after having an account with JAMR?</b><br>
			Yes you can become an author once you have uploaded your article and it has been approved by the editor.<br>
			<b>How can I become an author?</b><br>
			You can become an author by registering as a reader and then upload your article.<br>
			<b>Can I write a feedback letter on an author&#39;s article to the editor?</b><br>
			Yes you can write but you will have to register with JAMR first.<br>
			<b>How do I search for a specific article?</b><br>
			You can use the search bar on the top right corner and write the specific keywords. It can search by articles, authors and keywords.<br> 
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h4 class="panel-title">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">
