            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">
          	<b>How can I upload my article for publishing?</b><br>
          	<br>
		  	<b>Can I upload different versions of the articles?</b><br>
			<br>
			<b>How do I become a reviewer?</b><br>
			If uploads an article then automatically becomes a reviewer.<br>
			<b>How should I reply to the letter received from a reader through the editor?</b><br>
			<br>
			<b>What information is required when uploading an article?</b><br>
			Provide abstract, provide full author details and main contact, and provide a set of keywords.<br>
			<b>Do I need to revise the article?</b><br>
			Yes, you need to revise the article after the reviews.<br>
			<b>How many peer reviews are must?</b><br>
			Has to complete 3 peer reviews and re-review as well.<br>
			<b>Do I need to reply back to all criticism?</b><br>
			Yes, you have to reply back to each and every criticism by the reviewers.<br>
