      <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h4 class="panel-title">
            <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">
             Reviewer
            </a>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
          <div class="panel-body">
          	<b>Can I review only three articles?</b><br>
			Yes you can review three articles in order to get your article published.<br>

			<b>Can I only review the downloaded articles?</b><br>
			Yes you cannot review an article which you have not downloaded. You can only see the abstract if not downloaded. You can only download three unpublished articles for review.<br> 

			<b>Does my status change from reviewer to the author?</b><br>
			Yes, once he has reviewed the three articles and it has been accepted by the editor then he goes back to being an author only.<br>

			<b>Can I browse the pending articles?</b><br>
			No you cannot browse the unpublished articles. You can only see the abstract of the article until you select an article for review and download it.<br>

			<b>How many times will I have to review the same article?</b><br>
			You will not be asked more than twice to review the same article.<br>
          </div>
